# Super Admin Section Structure

The Super Admin section of the application provides comprehensive management interfaces for various aspects of the store. All Super Admin routes follow the pattern `/super-admin/*`.

## Directory Structure

The Super Admin pages are organized in the following structure:
- [src/app/(super-admin)/super-admin](mdc:src/app/(super-admin)/super-admin) - Contains all Super Admin pages
- [src/components/SuperAdmin](mdc:src/components/SuperAdmin) - Contains reusable components for the Super Admin section

## Authentication & Access Control

The Super Admin section requires authentication with admin privileges:

- Authentication is checked in [src/app/(super-admin)/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/(super-admin)/layout.tsx)
- The `/auth/self` API is used to verify admin access
- If authentication is missing or invalid, users are redirected to `/auth`
- When the API returns 401/403 errors or `isAdmin: false`, users are automatically redirected
- See [authentication-handling.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/authentication-handling.mdc) for the centralized auth error handling pattern

## Key Components

### Layout
- [src/app/(super-admin)/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/(super-admin)/layout.tsx) - The main layout wrapper for all Super Admin pages

### Sidebar Navigation
- [src/constants/superAdminSidebar.tsx](mdc:src/constants/superAdminSidebar.tsx) - Configuration for the sidebar menu items
- [src/components/SuperAdmin/Layout/Sidebar/index.tsx](mdc:src/components/SuperAdmin/Layout/Sidebar/index.tsx) - Sidebar component implementation

### Routes
- [src/utils/routes.ts](mdc:src/utils/routes.ts) - Contains all route definitions, including Super Admin routes

## Main Sections

The Super Admin interface consists of the following main sections:
- Dashboard (`/super-admin`) - Overview and statistics
- Products (`/super-admin/products`) - Product management
- Orders (`/super-admin/orders`) - Order management and monitoring
- Users (`/super-admin/users`) - User account management
- Carts (`/super-admin/carts`) - Shopping cart management
- Shipping (`/super-admin/shipping`) - Shipping options and regions
- Payment Methods (`/super-admin/payment-methods`) - Payment method configuration
- Coupons (`/super-admin/coupons`) - Promotional coupon management

## Common UI Components

The Super Admin interface utilizes several reusable components:
- Tables: [src/components/SuperAdmin/Table](mdc:src/components/SuperAdmin/Table) - Table components for data display
- Pagination: [src/components/SuperAdmin/Pagination](mdc:src/components/SuperAdmin/Pagination) - Pagination controls
- Layout components: [src/components/SuperAdmin/Layout](mdc:src/components/SuperAdmin/Layout) - Header, sidebar, and content wrappers

